image_analysis.description: A page from an OGE Form 278e, a public financial disclosure report for Donald J. Trump. This page, A9 of 47, lists various business entities (numbered 97 through 108) and details their ownership structure, including owners, percentage of ownership, and roles.
image_analysis.layout: A structured, single-column document with a header containing form information and the filer's name, a body listing entities and their ownership details in a repetitive format, and a footer with a document control number.
